<div class='talk-article__body talk-transcript__body'>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 0:11
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='599' id='t-599'>I've learned some of
my most important life lessons</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='5380' id='t-5380'>from drug dealers</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='7879' id='t-7879'>and gang members</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='10250' id='t-10250'>and prostitutes,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='12503' id='t-12503'>and I've had some of my most
